SIMPLE: measureless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Measureless
<hw>Meas"ure*less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without measure;
unlimited; immeasurable.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Meas"ure*less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Where Alf, the sacred river ran,⟦br⟧
Through canyons <qex>measureless</qex> to man,⟦br⟧
Down to a hidden sea.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Boundless; limitless; endless; unbounded;
unlimited; vast; immense; infinite; immeasurable.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Measurement</ent>⟦br⟧
